Package edu.gcu.cst341.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Superclass for creating Checking, Saving, and Loan accounts Future versions may declare this class abstract since it will not be instantiated
    Checking
    Child class of Account that creates Checking account objects
    Customer
    Customer class used to create Customer objects which will create Checking, Saving, and Loan objects NO LONGER NEEDS TO IMPLEMENT COMPARABLE BECAUSE THE APP WILL NO LONGER USE LISTS OF CUSTOMER OBJECTS
    Loan
    Class that inherits Account fields and behaviors and creates Loan object data and behaviors
    Saving
    Child class of Account that creates Saving account objects
    Transaction
    Class for logging banking transactions
